{"tid":2320032,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國PS官方贊助「Plash Speed 路由器」搞笑動畫短片團隊製作「空氣清新機」故事","createTime":"2020-12-10T13:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T08:56:55.000Z","uid":109923,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9be0d82c5a7fcf13b8d3522fb55b959064463105","tid":2320032,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:10:31.000Z","msg":"先前以一段丈夫瞞著妻子購買 PS4 Pro 主機卻被抓包的搞笑動畫短片「PlayStation（플레이스테이션）」帶動一波「Plash Speed 路由器」網路搞笑梗熱潮的韓國 Jangbbijju 工作室，今（10）日再度發表一段以最新上市之「PlayStation 5（PS5）」主機為題材的搞笑動畫短片新作「當面交易（직거래，直去來）」。<br />\n <br />\n  在這段短片中，之前被妻子抓包偷買 PS4 Pro 主機的丈夫，在替妻子面交拍賣物品時，赫然發現自己心愛的主機被妻子偷偷賤價賣給別人。究竟他要怎麼樣化解這樣的窘境呢？最後迎接他的又是什麼樣的結局呢？<br />\n  <br />\n<span class=\"red\">※ 相關影片為韓國 PlayStation 官方贊助製作<br />\n※ 影片包含內嵌繁體中文字幕，觀賞時請記得開啟</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eKB9KtH97OQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeKB9KtH97OQ&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqQ%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=eba1e39f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eKB9KtH97OQ</a>"},{"pid":"014feb8e2740e22930e65ca3715d282dd135357a","tid":2320032,"uid":109923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:13:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fTC5H67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfTC5H67.jpg&h=a91c0b96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ycZcn7u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FycZcn7u.jpg&h=dc0a0a35&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"821ba1c32288915dad3c1d211b59d9d2f17ec2e3","tid":2320032,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:22:08.000Z","msg":"好老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ab81265f7fc801024fda0b3e5ef6b1f6cdf9d8c","tid":2320032,"uid":123848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:35:43.000Z","msg":"跟住都係賣左你部PS5<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"